Use the standard library
This is how to reverse_delete of s and c:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that index is 0
  Do this s's length times:
    Remember that ch is item index in s
    When ch is not in c, then:
      Add result to ch
    End when
    Increase index by 1
  End do
  The answer is [result, 0]
